# JAQL Build System

Full reference: [docs/build-system.md](docs/build-system.md)

## Module Targets

```cmake
add_library(jaql_<module> ...)
add_library(jaql::<module> ALIAS jaql_<module>)
```

- `CXX_STANDARD 23`, `CXX_EXTENSIONS OFF`
- Public includes: `$<BUILD_INTERFACE:${PROJECT_SOURCE_DIR}/include>`
- Link only modules allowed by [docs/architecture/module-dependencies.md](docs/architecture/module-dependencies.md)

## Dependency Layers

Foundation → Domain → Analytics. Lower layers never depend on upper layers.

## Presets

| Preset | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `gcc-debug` | Daily development (ASan + UBSan) |
| `gcc-release` | Optimized local build |
| `ci-gcc-debug` | CI with coverage and `-Werror` |

Configure: `cmake --preset <name>`. Build: `cmake --build --preset <name>`.

## Conan

Dependencies managed via Conan 2 — see `conanfile.py` and `conan.lock`.
